From a8bd33020a7bf8e58fdc15d7c0db4a8fd6840cef Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Pranav Madhu <pranav.madhu@arm.com>
Date: Tue, 30 May 2023 22:15:18 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 31/78] Platform/ARM/SgiPkg: Add initial support for RD-V3-Cfg2
 platform

RD-V3-Cfg2 platform is quad chip configuration of RD-V3
platform, with 4 poseidon CPU per chip, with each chip having local
address mapping of 64GB per chip. Also each chip is equiped with 8GB
DRAM. This patch add initial support for RD-V3-Cfg2 platform.

Change-Id: Ib2c406dbfae6566693bd88f98ce462c1f4d0b969
Signed-off-by: Pranav Madhu <pranav.madhu@arm.com>
Signed-off-by: Nishant Sharma <nishant.sharma@arm.com>
